            </p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>ATS Resume Checker:</strong> Analyzes your resume for compatibility with Applicant Tracking Systems, providing a score and actionable recommendations. Your resume file is processed entirely in your browser and is never uploaded to our servers.</li>
              <li><strong>Portfolio Generator:</strong> Helps you create a professional portfolio website using customizable templates. All content is generated client-side and can be exported for self-hosting.</li>
              <li><strong>Salary Negotiation Toolkit:</strong> Provides salary benchmarks and negotiation strategies based on role, experience, and location data. All inputs remain on your device.</li>
              <li><strong>Interview Prep Coach:</strong> Offers practice questions and feedback frameworks for behavioral, technical, and situational interviews. Your responses are not recorded or stored on our servers.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              The Service is provided "as is" and is subject to change. We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any aspect of the Service at any time without prior notice. We are not obligated to maintain, support, or update any particular feature or tool.
